  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is filed under ProfileMinimal; a hash is present to support content integrity checking, but the digital signature has not yet been applied — the signature workflow is pending review by the responsible signatory authority. All 13 credibility factors are assessed or flagged. Decision outcome: Accepted (conditional on signature completion).",
