      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests must confirm theoretical convergence rates for all governing equations relevant to hemolysis transport at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing was performed only on simplified 2-D pipe flow; rotating impeller geometry was not included. Convergence rates for the hemolysis scalar transport equation were not verified independently. Achieved level 2."
    },
