      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics (e.g., E% or U95 band overlap) must be computed for all hemolysis QoIs against experimental data at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Comparisons were made graphically without formal statistical metrics. U95 uncertainty bands were not propagated through the hemolysis power-law model. Achieved level 2."
