      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for turbulence model selection and hemolysis power-law exponents must be supported by literature evidence or sensitivity analysis at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected without documented sensitivity comparison against alternative models (e.g., RSM). Power-law exponents were taken from Giersiepen et al. without uncertainty characterization. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1."
